ELEVATED Casual NEW AMERICAN FARE WITH NEW YORK CITY ROOTS
The Blue Dog Cookhouse and Bar
brings an elevated casual New York dining experience to Boca. Our rated chefs make use of top quality ingredients to give both classic and innovative dishes their best life. Our world renowned mixologists are committed to bringing an experience to Palm Beach County like it has never been experienced before. We are committed to quality you can depend upon, ingredients you can trust and service you will love.
Welcome to the New Boca experience where passion meets flavor.
